jam.plot
Class Action

java.lang.Object
  jam.plot.Action
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.event.ActionListener, CommandListener, java.util.EventListener, PlotMouseListener
public class Action
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, PlotMouseListener, CommandListener

Class the does the actions on plots. Receives commands from buttons and command line. Performs action by performing command on plot, plot1d and plot2d. Commands avaliable:

update
update a plot with current data
expand
expand channels to view
zoomin, zoomout
full
view all channles
linear, log
range
change the count range
auto
auto scale the count range
area
get an area
cancel

Version:
0.5
Author:
Ken Swartz
